game.name: Princess Foot Doctor
game.description:
Your favorite princess seems to be unlucky today. She has accidently met with an incident that brought her into a big trouble. Oh no! The princess got a severe foot injury and infection and she had no option rather than consulting a surgeon right away. Some of her family members have brought the lady to your hospital since you are one of the most popular foot doctor of the city. It is getting difficult for her to bear the pain. Help her now to recover from this unbearable pain and infection in Princess Foot Doctor. 

As a reputed foot doctor you have to take care of all the things that provide them with the needful and instant foot care. Do every possible effort to make her feel relaxed in this HTML5 doctor game! Once it is done, make sure to decorate her foot with the needful accessories and matching shoes. You would find all the medical tools and medicines on the left and right side of the screen. Pick up each tool one by one to treat the infected foot properly!

Do not forget to take an x-ray of her foot to check if her foot has any fracture. Clean the area with the medical solution and give her an injection to make her foot heal fast! Try to put every possible effort to make this Disney princess feel better! In case of getting bored, check out more doctor games for boys and girls on our website and allow yourself to learn about the commonly used medical equipment and terms. We are happy to get you connected with the best surgery games for girls that are playable on multiple devices without download.
